    <title>
      <string language="en">A Plethora of Polyhedra</string>
    </title>
    <language>en</language>
    <description>
      <string language="en">This is a free JAVA applet that helps users to study spatial geometry in a dynamic and interactive way. Using it, the user can rotate, zoom out, zoom in and translate a plethora of polyhedra. Moreover, the program is able to compute topological and geometrical duals of each polyhedron. Geometrical operations include unfolding, plane sections, truncation and stellation.</string>
    </description>
